 the adult star's send-off. A woman was a regular office lady when she had an affair with her boss. She quit her job however and subsequently met an old friend. She was connected to a new position being a counselor as a result. She would counsel men at the customers' houses. Clients are men who have no friends or families and suffer from sexual dysfunctions. She proved to be helpful.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.3199,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/6LnpaNLrPmvgdNqAg8ve1tipfsA.jpg","release_date":"2017-03-24","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":"/jyMXlhy8BF25RFycFjBPFWBZFVJ.jpg","original_title":"ぐしょ濡れ女神は今日もイク！","original_language":"ja"},{"id":595,"adult":false,"title":"To Kill a Mockingbird","video":false,"overview":"Scout Finch, 6, and her older brother Jem live in sleepy Maycomb, Alabama, spending much of their time with their friend Dill and spying on their reclusive and mysterious neighbor, Boo Radley. When Atticus, their widowed father and a respected lawyer, defends a black man named Tom Robinson against fabricated rape charges, the trial and tangent events expose the children to evils of racism and stereotyping.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":5.1662,"vote_count":2806,"poster_path":"/gZycFUMLx2110dzK3nBNai7gfpM.jpg","release_date":"1962-12-20","vote_average":7.994,"backdrop_path":"/zP6pqpSRRiOCjjC5oWKZKkHqoSB.jpg","original_title":"To Kill a Mockingbird","original_language":"en"},{"id":1253062,"adult":false,"title":"Phantasia","video":false,"overview":"X-ray images were invented in 1895, the same year in which the Lumière brothers presented their respective invention in what today is considered to be the first cinema screening. Thus, both cinema and radiography fall within the scopic regime inaugurated by modernity.  The use of X-rays on two sculptures from the Bilbao Fine Arts Museum generates images that reveal certain elements of them that would otherwise be invisible to our eyes. These images, despite being generally created for technical or scientific purposes, seem to produce a certain form of 'photogénie': they lend the radiographed objects a new appearance that lies somewhere between the material and the ethereal, endowing them with a vaporous and spectral quality. It is not by chance that physics and phantasmagoria share the term 'spectrum' in their vocabulary.","genre_ids":[99,16,18,27],"popularity":0.452,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/i5t3DM6ReBKGdjWECTEGMFGUcaO.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-13","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Phantasia","original_language":"xx"},{"id":854820,"adult":false,"title":"Junjō nurashi, aijō kurashi","video":false,"overview":"An erotic drama about an adolescent girl who grew up in a father-son family and grows up by noticing her father's free love. Tomomi, a high school girl who lost her mother when she was young and lives alone with her father's friend. Friend has been rigorously raising Tomomi with one man while holding multiple part-time jobs without getting a regular job, but Tomomi could not understand his father's feelings and was only repulsing. One day, Tomomi's best friend triggered an incident...","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.3709,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/2Ym9cTLFHqtDvKj44fetsYTbbXv.jpg","release_date":"2016-03-25","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":"/bJZapaG2Jt8Tgm4IqeMATrCpLGD.jpg","original_title":"純情濡らし、愛情暮らし","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1453267,"adult":false,"title":"Temptations of the Flesh","video":false,"overview":"A jilted housewife uncovers a horrifying secret about her husband when he tries her adobong puti.","genre_ids":[53,18],"popularity":0.344,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/55a1JMHXuD2GWV9ljScsW6GNXL2.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-19","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":"/vDL5vf5RSnAYO4DMgJrLuaksqx6.jpg","original_title":"TUKSONG LAMAN","original_language":"tl"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt5883008","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q28868415","instagram_id":null,"metacritic_id":"movie/wet-woman-in-the-w